        "timestamp": "2021-04-09 18:14:48.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 4:\n\n> Patch Set 4:\n> \n> When a merge is done to gerrit, how long before that is mirrored to github? There could be a delay so the csit may run against the last patch vs the latest patch.\n\nPer Jess, replication delay is \"1s\", so should be good enough. :-)",
        "patchset_number": 4
